                    <div class="wave" style="height: 300px; clip-path: polygon(0 40%, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%);"></div>
                    <div class="content" style="padding: 2rem 3rem;">
                        <h2 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6" style="font-size: 60pt;">ジャーニーマップの3層構造</h2>
                        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dbeafe 0%, #bfdbfe 100%); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                                <div style="background: #3b82f6; color: white; width: 60px; height: 60px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 28pt; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 2rem; flex-shrink: 0;">①</div>
                                <h3 style="font-size: 44pt; color: #1e40af;">行動レイヤー（青付箋）</h3>
                            </div>
                            <p style="font-size: 36pt; line-height: 1.6;">各STDCステージでの顧客の具体的行動を記録</p>
                        </div>
                        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7 0%, #fde68a 100%); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                                <div style="background: #f59e0b; color: white; width: 60px; height: 60px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 28pt; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 2rem; flex-shrink: 0;">②</div>
                                <h3 style="font-size: 44pt; color: #92400e;">感情レイヤー（黄付箋）</h3>
                            </div>
                            <p style="font-size: 36pt; line-height: 1.6;">各行動に対する感情温度を色でグラデーション表現</p>
                        </div>
                        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d1fae5 0%, #a7f3d0 100%); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                                <div style="background: #10b981; color: white; width: 60px; height: 60px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 28pt; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 2rem; flex-shrink: 0;">③</div>
                                <h3 style="font-size: 44pt; color: #065f46;">チャネルレイヤー（緑付箋）</h3>
                            </div>
                            <p style="font-size: 36pt; line-height: 1.6;">接点となるメディア・場所・タッチポイントを記録</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="script-box">
                            <p style="font-size: 36pt;">「3層構造：①行動②感情③チャネル。色で温度を塗るとボトルネックが浮きます。」</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

