                        </div>
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-6">
                            <div class="emotion-card border-l-4 border-green-500">
                                <div class="color-sample bg-green-500"><i class="fas fa-smile mr-2" style="font-size: 36pt;"></i><span style="font-size: 36pt;">好感・満足</span></div>
