                            </div>
                            <div class="emotion-card border-l-4 border-yellow-500">
                                <div class="color-sample bg-yellow-500"><i class="fas fa-meh mr-2" style="font-size: 36pt;"></i><span style="font-size: 36pt;">不安・迷い</span></div>
