                <div class="slide" id="slide6">
                    <div class="wave" style="height: 300px; clip-path: polygon(0 40%, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%);"></div>
                    <div class="wave" style="opacity: 0.5; height: 350px; clip-path: polygon(0 60%, 100% 20%, 100% 100%, 0% 100%);"></div>
                     <div class="content" style="padding: 2rem 3rem;">
                        <h2 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6" style="font-size: 60pt; line-height: 1.6;">KPIレイヤーで"測れる地図"に</h2>
                        <div class="mb-6"><h3 class="font-semibold text-blue-700 mb-4" style="font-size: 44pt; line-height: 1.6;">数値で体験を測定可能にする設計手法</h3></div>
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
                            <div class="kpi-card border-l-4 border-blue-500">
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-blue-700 mb-4 flex items-center" style="font-size: 36pt; line-height: 1.6;"><i class="fas fa-chart-line text-red-500 mr-3"></i>KPIで指標化する理由</h4>
                                <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-3" style="font-size: 28pt; line-height: 1.6;">
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 mt-1 mr-3"></i>測定できない体験は<span class="font-bold">改善できない</span></li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 mt-1 mr-3"></i>各セルに<span class="text-red-500 font-bold">赤付箋</span>でKPIを追加</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 mt-1 mr-3"></i>現状値と目標値を<span class="font-bold">両方</span>記載</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <div class="kpi-card border-l-4 border-red-500 relative">
                                <div class="sticky-note red-note absolute -top-3 -right-3" style="font-size:20pt; padding: 0.5rem;"><div class="font-bold">KPI Layer</div></div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-red-700 mb-4" style="font-size: 36pt; line-height: 1.6;">マップ完成イメージ</h4>
                                <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
                                    <div class="text-blue-600" style="font-size: 28pt; line-height: 1.6;">行動・感情・チャネル</div>
                                    <div class="text-2xl my-2" style="font-size: 28pt; line-height: 1.6;">+</div>
                                    <div class="font-bold text-red-600" style="font-size: 28pt; line-height: 1.6;">KPI (測定指標)</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-6">
                            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-4" style="font-size: 44pt; line-height: 1.6;"><i class="fas fa-bullseye text-red-500 mr-3"></i>各STDC段階の代表的KPI</h3>
                            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
                                <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center"><div class="font-bold text-blue-700 mb-3" style="font-size: 36pt;">See</div><div class="space-y-2"><div class="font-semibold" style="font-size: 28pt;">Impression</div><div style="font-size: 20pt;">ストーリービュー率</div><div class="text-red-600 font-bold" style="font-size: 28pt;">≧ 50%</div></div></div>
                                <div class="bg-yellow-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center"><div class="font-bold text-yellow-700 mb-3" style="font-size: 36pt;">Think</div><div class="space-y-2"><div class="font-semibold" style="font-size: 28pt;">Avg.Time</div><div style="font-size: 20pt;">平均滞在時間</div><div class="text-red-600 font-bold" style="font-size: 28pt;">≥ 1:30</div></div></div>
                                <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center"><div class="font-bold text-green-700 mb-3" style="font-size: 36pt;">Do</div><div class="space-y-2"><div class="font-semibold" style="font-size: 28pt;">CVR</div><div style="font-size: 20pt;">予約/クーポン率</div><div class="text-red-600 font-bold" style="font-size: 28pt;">≥ 3%</div></div></div>
                                <div class="bg-purple-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center"><div class="font-bold text-purple-700 mb-3" style="font-size: 36pt;">Care</div><div class="space-y-2"><div class="font-semibold" style="font-size: 28pt;">NPS</div><div style="font-size: 20pt;">推奨度スコア</div><div class="text-red-600 font-bold" style="font-size: 28pt;">≥ +25</div></div></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg border-l-8 border-blue-500 p-6 mb-6">
                            <div class="flex items-center mb-4"><i class="fas fa-lightbulb text-yellow-500 mr-4 text-5xl"></i><h3 class="font-bold text-blue-700" style="font-size: 44pt; line-height: 1.6;">赤付箋でのKPI設定方法</h3></div>
                            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                                <div class="bg-white rounded p-4"><div class="font-bold text-blue-700 mb-2" style="font-size: 36pt;">現状値を記載</div><div class="text-gray-700" style="font-size: 28pt;">例：現在のCVR 1.2%</div></div>
                                <div class="bg-white rounded p-4"><div class="font-bold text-red-700 mb-2" style="font-size: 36pt;">目標値を設定</div><div class="text-gray-700" style="font-size: 28pt;">例：目標CVR 3.0%</div></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="script-box"><p class="text-gray-700" style="font-size: 36pt; line-height: 1.6;">「指標を貼れば<span class="font-semibold">"測れる地図"完成</span>。数字がない施策は迷走します。」</p></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

