                    <div class="content" style="padding: 2rem 3rem;">
                        <h2 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6" style="font-size: 60pt; line-height: 1.6;">メインワークショップ：A3マップ作成</h2>
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-6">
                            <div class="md:col-span-1">
                                <div class="timer-box mb-6"><p class="font-medium opacity-80 mb-4" style="font-size: 28pt;">制限時間</p><div style="font-size: 72pt; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1;">25:00</div></div>
                                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm p-6">
                                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-700 mb-4 flex items-center" style="font-size: 36pt; line-height: 1.6;"><i class="fas fa-tools text-blue-500 mr-3"></i>必要な道具</h4>
                                    <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-3" style="font-size: 28pt; line-height: 1.6;"><li>• A3ワークシート</li><li>• 付箋4色セット</li><li>• 極太ペン</li></ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="md:col-span-2">
                                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6">
                                    <h3 class="font-bold text-blue-700 mb-6 flex items-center" style="font-size: 44pt; line-height: 1.6;"><i class="fas fa-list-ol mr-3"></i>4ステップ制作手順</h3>
                                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                                        <div class="flex items-start mb-6"><div class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0"><span class="font-bold" style="font-size: 24pt;">1</span></div><div><div class="sticky-note blue-note"><span class="font-bold" style="font-size: 20pt;">行動</span></div><p style="font-size: 28pt; color: #374151;">顧客行動を青付箋に記入</p></div></div>
                                        <div class="flex items-start mb-6"><div class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0"><span class="font-bold" style="font-size: 24pt;">2</span></div><div><div class="sticky-note yellow-note"><span class="font-bold" style="font-size: 20pt;">感情</span></div><p style="font-size: 28pt; color: #374151;">感情温度を黄付箋に記録</p></div></div>
                                        <div class="flex items-start mb-6"><div class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0"><span class="font-bold" style="font-size: 24pt;">3</span></div><div><div class="sticky-note green-note"><span class="font-bold" style="font-size: 20pt;">チャネル</span></div><p style="font-size: 28pt; color: #374151;">接点メディアを緑付箋に記入</p></div></div>
                                        <div class="flex items-start mb-6"><div class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0"><span class="font-bold" style="font-size: 24pt;">4</span></div><div><div class="sticky-note red-note"><span class="font-bold" style="font-size: 20pt;">KPI</span></div><p style="font-size: 28pt; color: #374151;">測定指標を赤付箋に記入</p></div></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="bg-yellow-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-yellow-400 p-4 mt-6">
                                        <h4 class="font-semibold text-yellow-800 mb-3 flex items-center" style="font-size: 36pt; line-height: 1.6;"><i class="fas fa-lightbulb text-yellow-500 mr-3"></i>ヒント</h4>
                                        <p class="text-gray-700" style="font-size: 28pt; line-height: 1.6;">赤色（ネガティブ感情）が固まるセルは改善ポイント。後で対策案を考えます。</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="script-box"><p class="text-gray-700" style="font-size: 36pt; line-height: 1.6;">「A3シートと4色付箋。手順①行動(青)→②感情(黄)→③チャネル(緑)→④KPI(赤)。残10・5・1分で声掛け。」</p></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

