                        <h2 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4" style="font-size: 60pt; line-height: 1.6;">講評：見えてきたギャップと秀逸アイデア</h2>
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-4">
                            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-4">
                                <div class="flex items-center mb-4"><div class="bg-red-100 text-red-600 rounded-full w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center mr-4"><i class="fas fa-search-minus text-2xl"></i></div><h3 class="font-bold text-red-600" style="font-size: 36pt; line-height: 1.6;">共通の弱点エリア</h3></div>
                                <div class="mb-4">
                                    <div class="journey-map" style="font-size: 12px;"> <div class="journey-cell text-blue-700 font-medium bg-blue-50">See</div><div class="journey-cell highlight-cell text-blue-700 font-medium bg-blue-50">Think ★</div><div class="journey-cell text-blue-700 font-medium bg-blue-50">Do</div><div class="journey-cell text-blue-700 font-medium bg-blue-50">Care</div>
                                        <div class="journey-cell">Paid</div><div class="journey-cell highlight-cell">Paid</div><div class="journey-cell">Paid</div><div class="journey-cell">Paid</div>
                                        <div class="journey-cell">Owned</div><div class="journey-cell highlight-cell">Owned</div><div class="journey-cell">Owned</div><div class="journey-cell">Owned</div>
                                        <div class="journey-cell">Earned</div><div class="journey-cell highlight-cell text-red-500 font-bold border-2 border-red-500">Earned ⚠️</div><div class="journey-cell">Earned</div><div class="journey-cell">Earned</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="bg-red-50 rounded-md border-l-4 border-red-400 p-3 mb-3">
                                    <h4 class="font-bold text-red-800 flex items-center mb-2" style="font-size: 28pt; line-height: 1.6;"><i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle mr-2"></i>"Think × Earned" が薄い</h4>
                                    <p class="text-gray-700" style="font-size: 20pt; line-height: 1.6;">多くの班で、情報検討段階でのオーガニックな評判形成が不足しています。</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-md flex items-start p-3">
